{"tid":1555674,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"跳閘果啲人其實都幾撚戇鳩","createTime":"2019-09-09T12:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T18:45:05.000Z","uid":174512,"like":31,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e75924edce26f7ce0b0eb46730905413d3b1e712","tid":1555674,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:16:30.000Z","msg":"識玩一定係撞閘<br />\n仲要次次都撞同一部閘機<br />\n舉個例<br />\n如果你平時係出開中環站A出口嘅<br />\n就認撚住其中一部機<br />\n然後次次出都撞果部<br />\n啲閘機撞得多會點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗我講啦<br />\n<br />\nBtw其實我唔係真係話跳閘果啲on9<br />\n大家兄弟爬山各有各做<br />\n不過跳都唔跳果啲就真係正宗on9 仔<br />\n講緊你啊垃圾<br />\n<br />\n願為吾城<br />\n焚我殘軀<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"0e8bbae56e3b2b0cea3fdd14cd6ef6525d47beea","tid":1555674,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:19:45.000Z","msg":"不要說推 試著說撞"},{"pid":"fdc3a162c0fda1907c4c26abdc3bb94ac31a9321","tid":1555674,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:19:55.000Z","msg":"撞"},{"pid":"e57950fdaad6b689e161dea62b0a25b12aab60b4","tid":1555674,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:20:12.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"cbf1b70c59a4562817817a71f65f3c09fc672ed6","tid":1555674,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:20:22.000Z","msg":"自撞十野"},{"pid":"0fd817e8721a48b2667d49d8e5b69585a80f95a9","tid":1555674,"uid":264996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:20:24.000Z","msg":"（集思廣益）連儂牆唔夠文宣之建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1555513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1555513</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9365be5dbc82a442e114d2f0327d07d2acc7bcfb","tid":1555674,"uid":174512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T12:21:06.000Z","msg":"其實我地咪就係維尼個fd跳跳虎囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\"